title: Readout of Secretary Carter's Meeting with Qatari Minister of State for Defense Affairs Hamad bin ...
text: ( Source : US Department of Defense ) Pentagon Press Secretary Peter Cook provided the following readout: Today , Secretary of Defense Ash Carter met with Qatari Minister of State for Defense Affairs Hamad bin Ali Al Attiyah at the Pentagon.
